---
title: Caramelized Brown Sugar Chicken with Succotash and Roasted Potatoes
description: The key to sticky sweet chicken is brown sugar! Watch as it perfectly caramelizes underneath the broiler. Roasted potatoes and succotash turn to this meal into a southern-inspired delight!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-caramelise-a-la-cassonade-a86f69bd.jpg
